data.description: Welcome to your gorgeous custom home  with views that stretches across the horizon.  Open floor plan offers plenty of possibilities or sit back and enjoy the sunset from your private backdoor oasis. Spacious lot surrounded by mountain views with walking, riding trails just minutes away.  Enjoy the backyard BBQ or cool off inside with the updated refrigerator air. Spacious master suite offers enjoyable experience with walk in closet. Fully fenced with oversized 3 car garage and plenty of parking and storage. Easy access to the Freeway, convenient to Albuquerque and surrounding areas. This property offers endless possibilities!
